  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><br>Resources are limited. Explore the map and harvest as much as you can.<br>Uset them to build facilities, hire talents and recruit troops.<br>Each type of facility has different set of creatures, plus distinctive set of structures to build.<br><br>You can play campaign, single scenario or multiplayer map.<br>To win a map, finish its main mission. To improve your final score, solve side tasks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game tempo is configurable</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> turn-based or real-time battles (several modes available)<br></li><li> real-time exploration<br></li><li> few pre-configured speeds to choose from</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Featuers</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore Zbukiland maps and discover hard to find secret locations.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552820/extras/71a3ee48ab12d324a984d52a21612c60.avif?t=1697482595\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gather and manage resources; use them to recruit troops and talents.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552820/extras/64e9b784b878b7fc4dda13ab34ee7d09.avif?t=1697482595\" width=600 height=288 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Lead your armies to victory</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552820/extras/a2afb591ad0d27cc95d8ffb23a814831.avif?t=1697482595\" width=600 height=253 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Be rewarded by elaborate scoring system.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2552820/extras/006f87a6a39b5b13e1fd4cd4d8ef5c53.avif?t=1697482595\" width=600 height=332 /></span><br><br>Have fun and let the Zbuki be with you!",
